<h1 align="center" id="title">Covid-19 Data Visualisation Project</h1>

<p align="center"><img src="https://github.com/Theshruvie/Data-visualisation-projects.git" alt="project-image"></p>

<p id="description">This Colab project visualizes COVID-19 data using Plotly Seaborn and Matplotlib. It explores trends in confirmed cases deaths and recoveries globally and within specific regions. Interactive Plotly graphs allow for detailed exploration while Seaborn and Matplotlib provide static insights into data distributions and relationships offering a comprehensive view of the pandemic's impact.</p>
